            <title>[LU-987] Fail to create ldisk rpms RHEL5</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-987</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current build system for lustre will compile ldiskfs but a make rpms will fail. This is due to the BUILD_SERVER variable not being set in the autoMakefile&lt;/p&gt;</description>
